# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Ghostty Configuration - 2026 AI Era
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#
# Theme: Catppuccin Mocha (consistent with Neovim + Starship)
# Font:  Hack Nerd Font Mono
# Shell: Fish 4.6+ with Starship prompt
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

auto-update-channel = tip

# ─── Font ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

font-family = "Hack Nerd Font Mono"
font-size = 24
font-feature = -calt
font-feature = -liga
font-feature = -dlig
font-synthetic-style = false

# ─── Cursor (vibrant pink from catppuccin) ────────────────────────────────────

cursor-color = #f5c2e7
cursor-text = #11111b
cursor-opacity = 1.0
cursor-style = block
cursor-style-blink = false

# ─── Window & Appearance ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

macos-titlebar-style = tabs
macos-option-as-alt = true
macos-window-shadow = true
macos-non-native-fullscreen = false
window-colorspace = display-p3
window-padding-x = 12
window-padding-y = 12
window-padding-balance = true
window-padding-color = extend
window-theme = auto
window-save-state = always
window-new-tab-position = current
window-inherit-font-size = true
fullscreen = true
resize-overlay = after-first
scrollbar = never

# Translucent glass effect (titlebar inherits this look)
background-opacity = 0.90
background-blur = true

# Split appearance (catppuccin mocha colors)
unfocused-split-opacity = 0.65
unfocused-split-fill = #11111b
split-divider-color = #313244
focus-follows-mouse = false

# ─── Keyboard ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

mouse-hide-while-typing = true
keybind = shift+enter=text:\n
keybind = ctrl+enter=text:\n
keybind = cmd+enter=text:\n
keybind = global:cmd+shift+space=toggle_quick_terminal

# macOS standard
keybind = cmd+n=new_window
keybind = cmd+t=new_tab
keybind = cmd+w=close_surface

# Font size
keybind = cmd+plus=increase_font_size:1
keybind = cmd+minus=decrease_font_size:1
keybind = cmd+zero=reset_font_size

# ─── Pane Management (vim-style) ─────────────────────────────────────────────

keybind = cmd+d=new_split:right
keybind = cmd+shift+d=new_split:down
keybind = cmd+|=new_split:right
keybind = cmd+shift+minus=new_split:down

# performable: pass to app (Neovim) when no splits exist
keybind = performable:ctrl+h=goto_split:left
keybind = performable:ctrl+j=goto_split:bottom
keybind = performable:ctrl+k=goto_split:top
keybind = performable:ctrl+l=goto_split:right

keybind = cmd+shift+enter=toggle_split_zoom
keybind = cmd+ctrl+=equalize_splits
split-preserve-zoom = navigation

# Key table: Ctrl+W → R for resize mode, h/j/k/l to adjust, Esc to exit
keybind = ctrl+w>r=activate_key_table:resize
keybind = resize/h=resize_split:left,10
keybind = resize/j=resize_split:down,10
keybind = resize/k=resize_split:up,10
keybind = resize/l=resize_split:right,10
keybind = resize/escape=deactivate_key_table

# ─── Tab Management ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

keybind = cmd+shift+]=next_tab
keybind = cmd+shift+[=previous_tab

# ─── Window Navigation ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

keybind = cmd+shift+right=goto_window:next
keybind = cmd+shift+left=goto_window:previous

# ─── Clipboard ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

clipboard-read = allow
clipboard-write = allow
clipboard-trim-trailing-spaces = true
copy-on-select = true
clipboard-paste-protection = true
keybind = cmd+shift+c=copy_to_clipboard:html

# ─── Shell Integration ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

shell-integration = fish
shell-integration-features = no-cursor,sudo,title
window-inherit-working-directory = true
tab-inherit-working-directory = true
split-inherit-working-directory = true

# Prompt-to-prompt jump
keybind = ctrl+shift+up=jump_to_prompt:-1
keybind = ctrl+shift+down=jump_to_prompt:1
cursor-click-to-move = true

# ─── Scrollback & Navigation ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

scrollback-limit = 100000

keybind = ctrl+u=scroll_page_fractional:-0.5
keybind = alt+b=scroll_page_up
keybind = alt+g=scroll_to_top
keybind = alt+shift+g=scroll_to_bottom

# ─── AI Workflow ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Auto-scroll on AI streaming output
scroll-to-bottom = keystroke,output

# Clear selection on typing (reduce noise during AI output review)
selection-clear-on-typing = true
selection-clear-on-copy = true

# Save terminal screen to file (useful for long Claude Code output)
keybind = cmd+shift+s=write_screen_file:open,plain

# Toggle mouse reporting for TUI apps
keybind = cmd+shift+m=toggle_mouse_reporting

# ─── Notifications & Misc ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

link-url = true
link-previews = true
bold-is-bright = true
confirm-close-surface = true
desktop-notifications = true
bell-features = title,attention
minimum-contrast = 1.2
title-report = false
enquiry-response =
image-storage-limit = 320000000

# Notify on long command completion (when terminal unfocused)
notify-on-command-finish = unfocused
notify-on-command-finish-after = 5s
notify-on-command-finish-action = bell,notify

# Quick Terminal (drop-down)
quick-terminal-position = top
quick-terminal-animation-duration = 0.2
quick-terminal-autohide = true

# Environment
env = GHOSTTY=1

# ─── Catppuccin Mocha Theme ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# https://github.com/catppuccin/ghostty

background = #1e1e2e
foreground = #cdd6f4
selection-foreground = #1e1e2e
selection-background = #cba6f7

search-foreground = #11111b
search-background = #f9e2af
search-selected-foreground = #11111b
search-selected-background = #fab387

palette-generate = false
palette = 0=#45475a
palette = 1=#f38ba8
palette = 2=#a6e3a1
palette = 3=#f9e2af
palette = 4=#89b4fa
palette = 5=#f5c2e7
palette = 6=#94e2d5
palette = 7=#a6adc8
palette = 8=#585b70
palette = 9=#f38ba8
palette = 10=#a6e3a1
palette = 11=#f9e2af
palette = 12=#89b4fa
palette = 13=#f5c2e7
palette = 14=#94e2d5
palette = 15=#bac2de
